lex:D0860\/Artigo2\/IncisoIII    lex:temIncisoAlinea    lex:D0860\/Artigo2\/IncisoIII\/IncisoAlineaConfederacao .
lex:D0860\/Artigo2\/IncisoIII\/IncisoAlineaConfederacao    lex:temConteudo    "a) Confederação Nacional da Agricultura (CNA);" .
lex:D0860\/Artigo2\/IncisoIII\/IncisoAlineaConfederacao\/IncisoAlineaConfederacao    lex:ehUm    lex:IncisoAlinea .
lex:D0860\/Artigo2\/IncisoIII\/IncisoAlineaConfederacao    lex:temIncisoAlinea    lex:D0860\/Artigo2\/IncisoIII\/IncisoAlineaConfederacao\/IncisoAlineaConfederacao .
lex:D0860\/Artigo2\/IncisoIII\/IncisoAlineaConfederacao\/IncisoAlineaConfederacao    lex:temConteudo    "b) Confederação Nacional do Comércio (CNC);" .
lex:D0860\/Artigo2\/IncisoIII\/IncisoAlineaConfederacao\/IncisoAlineaConfederacao\/IncisoAlineaConfederacao    lex:ehUm    lex:IncisoAlinea .
lex:D0860\/Artigo2\/IncisoIII\/IncisoAlineaConfederacao\/IncisoAlineaConfederacao    lex:temIncisoAlinea    lex:D0860\/Artigo2\/IncisoIII\/IncisoAlineaConfederacao\/IncisoAlineaConfederacao\/IncisoAlineaConfederacao .
lex:D0860\/Artigo2\/IncisoIII\/IncisoAlineaConfederacao\/IncisoAlineaConfederacao\/IncisoAlineaConfederacao    lex:temConteudo    "c) Confederação Nacional da Indústria (CNI);" .
lex:D0860\/Artigo2\/IncisoIII\/IncisoAlineaConfederacao\/IncisoAlineaConfederacao\/IncisoAlineaConfederacao\/IncisoAlineaConfederacao    lex:ehUm    lex:IncisoAlinea .
