lex:D0860\/Artigo2\/IncisoIII\/IncisoAlineaConfederacao\/IncisoAlineaConfederacao\/IncisoAlineaConfederacao\/IncisoAlineaConfederacao    lex:temConteudo    "d) Confederação Nacional do Transporte (CNT);" .
lex:D0860\/Artigo2\/IncisoIII\/IncisoAlineaConfederacao\/IncisoAlineaConfederacao\/IncisoAlineaConfederacao\/IncisoAlineaConfederacao\/IncisoAlineaFederacao    lex:ehUm    lex:IncisoAlinea .
